Frequently Asked Questions General How can i get the version number of Fore at runtime? Open a console in the devtools of your browser, enter this line and hit return:
document.querySelector(&#39;fx-fore&#39;).version This will output something like:
&lsquo;Version: 1.7.1 - built on September 28, 2023 13:52:58&rsquo;
